Captain Sir Humphrey de Trafford BT. M.C.
Coldstream Guards
Born 1891 - Died 1971
And two of his sons-in-law

Major General Sir James Bowes-Lyon
KCVO CB OBE MC
Grenadier Guards
Born 1917 - Died 1977

And

Derek Parker Bowles 
Royal Horse Guards
Born 1915 - Died 1977"©
