from the members of the Brixton Dog Training Club"į
≠It was on this bench in 2007 that the notorious artist Tracey Emin surrendered all her art rebel credibility when she decided to become a member of the Royal Academy of Arts"Ī
ģTo Baby Angelina
Our Beautiful angel, Our hearts are filled with sorrow for having left us so soon
We love you; Miss you every moment of everyday
Mum. Dad. Sister & Family"≤
ĮDAVID BUCKNELL (DJB) 1939 - 2004
Bon viveur, raconteur, tin collector extraordinaire
was born to retire and went to Paradise by way of
Kensal Green (and a hostelry or two!)"∂
